# Telegram Shop Pro

Production-grade refactor of the legacy Telegram shop bot, keeping the original business flows while hardening transactions, payment reconciliation, observability and Windows desktop operations.

## What This Project Keeps
- `/start`, `/help`, `/getchatid`, `/checkadmin`
- Inline user menu and hidden admin panel
- Categories, products, stock control, coupon flow, purchase history
- Referral/affiliate flow with `start=ref_<user_id>`
- Optional `/start` video
- VietQR pending deposit flow with admin approve/reject buttons
- Auto bank polling through Coderent history API
- Deposit logs, order logs, admin notifications, broadcast
- Windows desktop GUI with dark mode, config save/load, start/stop bot, start/stop bank poller, real-time logs

## Improvements Added
- Transaction-safe purchase flow
- Safer manual/auto deposit reconciliation to avoid double credit
- SQLite WAL mode, busy timeout, migrations and compatibility columns
- Structured logging to console, file and GUI
- Separate runtime controls for bot and bank poller
- Dashboard stats in GUI
- CSV export and DB backup helpers
- Automated tests for order, coupon, deposit and affiliate services

