## Deploy / Packaging Notes
- For a Windows desktop package, PyInstaller can bundle `python scripts\run_gui.py`.
- For 24/7 headless operation, use `python scripts\run_bot.py` under NSSM, Task Scheduler or another Windows service wrapper.
- Keep the machine online for polling and Telegram delivery.

